  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5801722">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5801722/" class="title-link">1976年版的《论十大关系》是伪作</a>
